Handshake,is,a,service,for,writing,and,receiving,orders,online,using,an,iPad,iPhone,or,web,browser,Orders,sync,instantly,and,are,automatically,tracked,and,sorted,by,item,region,rep,and,more,Customer,lists,and,information,are,managed,so,that,important,information,such,as,order,history,is,always,within,easy,reach,Handshake,even,comes,with,support,for,barcode,scanning,The,Handshake,API,enables,users,to,integrate,Handshake,with,other,applications,and,services,using,REST,calls,issued,in,XML,or,JSON